messages.messageBody:
I am tired, and realized I haven't recovered as emotionally as I thought I
had. I'm also feeling a little anemic, so that doesn't help. I'm going to
take a break from this list for a while, not going to unsub, just going on no
mail for a bit. Its my fault for not listening to myself sooner, and I let
some things get to me, shared things I normally wouldn't have, and replied to
some things I would have normally just let slide on by. <g> So for now, I
will see where this takes me. I'll see some of you in the quiet backroom.

Much love to you all,
~Nancy


[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
